1
00:00:06,570 --> 00:00:11,950
♪Obsessions penned
into an everlasting love♪

2
00:00:12,330 --> 00:00:17,580
♪Affections gently linger
around fingertips♪

3
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:23,140
♪May stars guide us through rough waves♪

4
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:28,520
♪I give all my love unreservedly♪

5
00:00:29,030 --> 00:00:30,900
♪May transient frost♪

6
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,690
♪Persist through obstacles for love♪

7
00:00:34,820 --> 00:00:40,330
♪I wait for you to look back
in this rocky life♪

8
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:42,550
♪I can stay for the promise♪

9
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:46,180
♪Despite seasons recur♪

10
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:51,760
♪The love deep within
will transcend time♪

11
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:57,500
[Secrets of the Shadow Sect]

12
00:00:57,540 --> 00:01:00,820
[Episode 2]

13
00:01:07,380 --> 00:01:08,180
I want you.

14
00:01:11,020 --> 00:01:12,140
It's rare that shadow guards

15
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:13,660
have a good-looking face like yours.

16
00:01:13,980 --> 00:01:15,780
Since you offered yourself here,

17
00:01:16,420 --> 00:01:17,780
how could I

18
00:01:17,980 --> 00:01:19,300
turn you down?

19
00:01:25,220 --> 00:01:26,420
I, Yingshi, the shadow guard,

20
00:01:26,420 --> 00:01:28,060
will serve you as my master for life

21
00:01:28,100 --> 00:01:29,220
and always be at your disposal.

22
00:01:29,300 --> 00:01:30,220
Never betray you.

23
00:01:35,260 --> 00:01:36,300
Get up.

24
00:01:39,300 --> 00:01:40,180
Thank you, Master.

25
00:01:40,420 --> 00:01:41,380
Ling'er.

26
00:01:44,020 --> 00:01:45,180
Young Master.

27
00:01:45,180 --> 00:01:47,380
Prepare a room in the inner yard
for him.

28
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,660
Starting from today,

29
00:01:48,660 --> 00:01:50,820
he will stay in Xuantian House.

30
00:01:51,220 --> 00:01:52,020
Yes.

31
00:01:53,020 --> 00:01:54,060
Oh, right.

32
00:01:56,020 --> 00:01:57,460
Just now, I said

33
00:01:57,460 --> 00:01:59,500
the Xuantian House only keeps beauties,

34
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:00,700
not guards.

35
00:02:00,820 --> 00:02:01,980
It wasn't an excuse.

36
00:02:02,700 --> 00:02:04,260
From now on,

37
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:07,500
tell everyone you belong to me.
What do you say?

38
00:02:11,820 --> 00:02:12,820
No?

39
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:18,180
Anything you say.

40
00:02:30,380 --> 00:02:32,020
She's just as ridiculous as rumored.

41
00:02:36,850 --> 00:02:38,870
[First Class, Yingshi]

42
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:16,940
Young Master, your handwriting

43
00:03:16,940 --> 00:03:18,020
has long surpassed Madam.

44
00:03:18,020 --> 00:03:19,260
You have your own style.

45
00:03:20,660 --> 00:03:21,900
It's getting late.

46
00:03:22,100 --> 00:03:23,900
Please get rest early.

47
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:27,740
Young Master.

48
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:29,860
There are some sects in trouble again.

49
00:03:30,740 --> 00:03:32,860
The entire sect disappeared,

50
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:35,180
and their martial arts manuals
have gone missing.

51
00:03:35,300 --> 00:03:37,420
This is the second time this month,
right?

52
00:03:37,420 --> 00:03:39,780
Yes, Young Master.

53
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:42,140
It was the same

54
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:43,740
before Madam had the accident.

55
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:46,140
Master Ling needs the assistance of
Madam's technique

56
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:48,740
to combine martial arts skills
from all sects.

57
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:51,140
Fortunately, Madam

58
00:03:51,140 --> 00:03:53,020
passed on the secret manual
to you in advance.

59
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:57,820
The Pipa player
was sent to assassinate.

60
00:03:58,340 --> 00:03:59,740
I'm afraid they are getting impatient.

61
00:04:02,620 --> 00:04:03,940
My dear father.

62
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:06,860
People think he is
an unconcerned martial arts enthusiast.

63
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:10,100
Little do they know he wants to dominate
the martial arts world.

64
00:04:10,780 --> 00:04:13,140
We must stop him

65
00:04:14,060 --> 00:04:15,460
before the bloodshed breaks out.

66
00:04:16,540 --> 00:04:17,180
Mr. Ya.

67
00:04:17,820 --> 00:04:19,660
Search for those missing members
in secret.

68
00:04:19,660 --> 00:04:22,140
I will take care of that Pipa player
before that.

69
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:23,340
No.

70
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:26,060
Send Yingshi

71
00:04:26,860 --> 00:04:28,460
to handle her.

72
00:04:47,340 --> 00:04:49,060
Even the clothes are tacky.

73
00:05:23,740 --> 00:05:24,940
You came this late at night.

74
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:26,660
Is there any order from Master?

75
00:06:26,700 --> 00:06:27,500
Master.

76
00:06:32,420 --> 00:06:34,300
Young Master allows Yingshi to stay

77
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:36,220
and takes him in.

78
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,060
Apart from that,

79
00:06:38,580 --> 00:06:39,540
according to your order,

80
00:06:39,540 --> 00:06:40,460
I have sent members of
the Danyang Pavilion

81
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:41,620
and Tianxing Tower

82
00:06:41,820 --> 00:06:42,980
to Medicine King Valley.

83
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:44,780
Fortunately,

84
00:06:44,940 --> 00:06:46,700
I have found their martial arts manuals.

85
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:53,700
Are you sure

86
00:06:54,540 --> 00:06:56,620
that the shadow guard you sent out

87
00:06:57,700 --> 00:06:59,660
can complete the task?

88
00:07:00,220 --> 00:07:01,260
Don't worry.

89
00:07:01,660 --> 00:07:02,860
Since he joined the sect
as a little boy,

90
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:04,580
he has been taking

91
00:07:04,580 --> 00:07:05,620
the Soul-shattering Pills

92
00:07:05,860 --> 00:07:07,820
every month

93
00:07:07,940 --> 00:07:09,100
without interruption.

94
00:07:21,780 --> 00:07:23,220
You just get up.

95
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:25,980
But why does your hand feel cold?

96
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:29,380
No one cares or loves me.

97
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:30,980
Naturally, they are cold.

98
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:34,020
You must be joking.

99
00:07:34,460 --> 00:07:35,900
Many people in the Xuantian House

100
00:07:36,220 --> 00:07:37,420
are dying

101
00:07:37,420 --> 00:07:38,580
to see you.

102
00:07:39,020 --> 00:07:40,180
If you don't mind

103
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:41,100
my lowly status.

104
00:07:41,820 --> 00:07:43,460
I'm willing to give you my heart

105
00:07:43,860 --> 00:07:45,460
without hesitation.

106
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:47,900
Very well.

107
00:07:49,220 --> 00:07:51,420
I will have someone dig your heart out.

108
00:07:51,460 --> 00:07:52,820
All right?

109
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:54,060
Young Master.

110
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:55,620
Please spare my life, Young Master.

111
00:07:55,620 --> 00:07:56,900
I will take my leave now.

112
00:08:01,460 --> 00:08:02,260
What's the matter?

113
00:08:02,460 --> 00:08:05,380
Yingshi didn't kill the Pipa player
last night.

114
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:07,740
Noted.

115
00:08:08,300 --> 00:08:09,420
You may go.

116
00:08:09,900 --> 00:08:10,620
Yes.

117
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:31,820
Master.

118
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:33,820
You are back.

119
00:08:34,940 --> 00:08:35,740
Come.

120
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:37,100
Sit here.

121
00:08:47,060 --> 00:08:48,900
Look, cold dews are all over you.

122
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:50,340
Your garment is damp.

123
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:52,460
Didn't I ask Ling'er

124
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:54,300
to deliver the male escort's clothes
yesterday?

125
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:55,540
Why didn't you put that on?

126
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:57,620
I just returned

127
00:08:58,140 --> 00:08:59,700
and came here to report.

128
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:01,740
I haven't had time to change.

129
00:09:11,300 --> 00:09:12,020
Why?

130
00:09:12,740 --> 00:09:14,020
You mess up

131
00:09:14,460 --> 00:09:15,260
such a simple task?

132
00:09:16,220 --> 00:09:17,260
Speaking of this,

133
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:18,740
I have looked into

134
00:09:18,740 --> 00:09:20,460
the mastermind behind the Pipa player.

135
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:22,540
She was instructed

136
00:09:22,540 --> 00:09:23,580
to assassinate you while you were drunk

137
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:25,540
by Madam Yu from the Cangyu Abode.

138
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:26,420
Besides,

139
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:27,740
she revealed all the spies Madam planted

140
00:09:27,740 --> 00:09:29,380
in the Xuantian House.

141
00:09:30,260 --> 00:09:31,260
Here's the list.

142
00:09:33,860 --> 00:09:34,580
How did you find out

143
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:36,420
about these?

144
00:09:40,060 --> 00:09:40,860
Please don't kill me.

145
00:09:41,100 --> 00:09:42,300
[Fubao]
The Pipa player's husband died early

146
00:09:42,380 --> 00:09:43,140
and left her with a son,

147
00:09:43,300 --> 00:09:44,580
who is then kidnapped by Madam Yu.

148
00:09:44,700 --> 00:09:45,740
She was forced

149
00:09:45,740 --> 00:09:46,700
to assassinate you.

150
00:09:46,900 --> 00:09:47,780
I discovered

151
00:09:47,780 --> 00:09:49,420
her son is locked
in a house in the city.

152
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:00,940
Very well done.

153
00:10:01,380 --> 00:10:03,060
How should I reward you, then?

154
00:10:04,460 --> 00:10:06,660
She committed this crime
to keep her child safe.

155
00:10:07,180 --> 00:10:08,780
I believe her crime
doesn't warrant death.

156
00:10:09,180 --> 00:10:11,460
So I took the liberty to spare her life.

157
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:19,700
♪If hand waves are
the prelude to farewell♪

158
00:10:20,140 --> 00:10:23,300
♪If words hold no intention to stall♪

159
00:10:23,860 --> 00:10:25,580
♪Goodbye♪

160
00:10:25,780 --> 00:10:29,620
♪Should be reserved
for when our lives are at stake♪

161
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:34,230
♪If time rushes swiftly
like wind and dust♪

162
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:37,940
♪If tears come before words
after waking up♪

163
00:10:38,340 --> 00:10:40,620
♪May you not be drowned in bitterness♪

164
00:10:40,940 --> 00:10:42,220
♪I only wish your eyes♪

165
00:10:42,380 --> 00:10:45,300
♪As pure as snow♪
